  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then [INAUDIBLE] everybody went to, to to near the-- the [NON-ENGLISH] there was a-- a bath house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right near they was doing the kashruting the pots and pans before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The kids had a good time and running around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was their excitement, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then when we ate of [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pesach, ?] breaking the matzahs was a very, very spiritual thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Almost the whole town was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't this one bakery, and the same, the [INAUDIBLE] for the baking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was all spiritual.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was lifted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was a new person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This, you cannot describe those in words, the feeling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was like a new-- you came into a new atmosphere completely, especially Pesach.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The kids were wearing those-- those new clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they looked at those shoes, and they went like this, to wipe off in case a little spot went because it was once a year that put the shoes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the little suit [INAUDIBLE] they had on, they was-- they were shining.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was-- in poverty, that was things that-- that everybody almost felt, now everybody's rich almost.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Especially the kids felt so different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was something that you can-- could touch it with your hand if you wanted to observe it, if your eyes caught it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you weren't always used to it or you want to observe it, you had that feeling, that great feeling, that even the poor felt good.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no any plan for the future.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, four or five-- up to about four or five years before the war, you came in-- especially a-- a winter night-- you came into beth midrash.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the club.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
